# Using NUC

Connect telephone for Wifi
Connect NUC to Odroid with wire

On PC:
sshfs mpelcat@192.168.43.24:/ ~/Temp/nuc

# Setting up project
rm -R ~/Temp/nuc/home/mpelcat/Projets/preesm-private/org.ietr.preesm.experiment.odroid.moa1
cp -R ~/Projets/preesm-private/org.ietr.preesm.experiment.odroid.moa1 ~/Temp/nuc/home/mpelcat/Projets/preesm-private

On PC tab 2
ssh mpelcat@192.168.43.24
sshfs odroid@192.168.0.2:/ ~/Temp/odroid

On PC tab 3
ssh mpelcat@192.168.43.24
ssh odroid@192.168.0.2

On the NUC:
cd ~/Projets/preesm-private/org.ietr.preesm.experiment.odroid.moa1/Code/scripts
tmux
./experiment1 ...
Ctrl+B D
log off
#on return
tmux attach

screen -r            #resume the screen session

To retrieve data on PC:
cp -R ~/Temp/nuc/home/mpelcat/Projets/preesm-private/org.ietr.preesm.experiment.odroid.moa1/finalstats/mat/activity/03-07-2016/* ~/Projets/preesm-private/org.ietr.preesm.experiment.odroid.moa1/finalstats/mat/activity/03-07-2016


cp .ssh/id_rsa2.pub ~/Temp/odroid/home


